# Marketing Copy & UX Tone

- Tone: clear, confident, specific; avoid hype and vague superlatives.
- Hero: outcome-led headline (≤ 8 words), supportive subhead (≤ 20), 3 concise benefits.
- CTAs: 1 primary action per screen; verbs that imply value (e.g., "Start free").
- Accessibility: readable contrast, descriptive alt text, meaningful link labels.
